description:
Danny welcome Kameron Westcott from The Real Housewives of Dallas to the show to wrap up season 3 of the show. He also recaps the most recent episode of #RHONJ, and honors talk show queen Kathie Lee Gifford.


Kameron Westcott Interview-- 11:40

#RHONJ Recap-- 33:00ish
